Text.string: This won't even be a challenge!
There's a badass in my way!
We're a good team, Vault Hunter!
Step up and get smacked down!
Let's do it again some time.
Not gonna die on my watch!
Let's get you back in the fight!
Come on, get your ass back up.
This is no time for a nap!
Let's get you back on the hunt.
So this is how the alpha does, huh?
Shouldn't your pet be doing this?
What, you think you're on leave?
Big bad Vault Hunter needed my help! (snicker)
Come on! Get back to it!
Let's get back to the fight!
You can't hunt from down there!
Is there a field medic in the house?
Hey, die on your own time!
I spy with my little eye...
How'd they bring down a Siren?
What you got?! You ain't got shit!
Take this! And that! And this too!
I'm gonna get zen over... here.
Ready to go when you are.
Go on, I'm right behind you.
I'm hit! A lot of times!
I'm good! Back to the fight!
Just needed a breather! I'm back!
Back on my feet! Let's go!
